  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.5.8">
<l>uṇṭā yulakēḻ muṉṉamē yumiḻntu māyai yālpuk</l>
<l>kuṇṭāy veṇṇey ciṟumaṉica ruvalai yākkai nilaiyeyti</l>
<l>maṇṭāṉ cōrnta tuṇṭēlu maṉicark kākum pīrciṟitu</l>
<l>maṇṭā vaṇṇa maṇkaraiya neyyūṇ maruntō māyōṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You ate the seven worlds once, after having spit [them] out. Having entered by magic,</l>
<l>reaching a position in the frail body of small humans you ate the butter,</l>
<l>even though the earth itself slipped [out] it is for the humans. So that the earth was dissolved</l>
<l>in a manner that a little white was [still] there, [was] eating butter the remedy, o Dark one?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
